        <num>CCP 3829</num>
        <heading>3829.  Notice of hearing</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3829.  Notice of hearing
When a person is in custody by virtue of a prior court order, or at the request of any person, reasonable written notice of the hearing shall be given to the person who provoked the prior court order or requested the custody.</p>
        </content>
